*Spomenuo* je svoj problem u vezi rada. (He mentioned his problem concerning work.)
*Spomenuše* su njihove nedavne aktivnosti. (Their recent activities were mentioned.)
*Spomenu* li se njegovo ime? (Is his name mentioned?)
*Spomenuće* se sigurno. (It will definitely be mentioned.)
*Spomenuo* sam da bi trebalo da se sastanemo. (I mentioned that we should meet.)